notesStmt.note: This service encounter takes place in a university office between a student advisor for international students and four exchange students (S3 leaves shortly after the beginning of the conversation). The student advisor explains matters which are essential for the exchange students at the beginning of their stay: e.g., where to pay the student fees, where to register, where to get certain forms, whom to ask when questions arise etc. There is frequent use of German, the language of their host country.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
